tags: I literally just scooted my ass down to Time Square
title: BTS IN TIME SQUARE
body: I literally just scooted my ass down to time square to see BTS. I’m just like, for what?! I missed them by 5 minutes! LITERALLY! Even if I would have just been cheering from outside the window, on the second floor, it all counts. At least I think so. So.. anyways, I stuck around, and this TS Officer that had informed me, also walked up and came to have a conversation with me. What an interesting day…
